            <title>[CASSANDRA-1408] nodetool drain attempts to delete a deleted file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1408</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running `nodetool drain` presented me with a pretty stack-trace.&lt;br/&gt;
